title: Drive Open v1.0 (Annoying and Funny)
description:
This is a very annoying application to run.
It opens every 60 seconds all of your cd and/or dvd drives on your pc/laptop.
The program runs in the background and don't need to be runned with special privileges.
The goal of this program is ........... I have no idea, but maybe you can use it to piss of your brother/sister, parents or your teacher.

You can stop this program by clicking crtl/alt/del and then close the task Drive Open.
